This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image style transfer. Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of graph cut formulation in the paper suggests that it could also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) category. Finally, the paper involves the transfer of multiple styles, which suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
